trans-unit.source: Specifies the available verbosity levels of a <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Utilities.Logger"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Anger hur tillgängliga nivåer av en <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Utilities.Logger"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The descriptions of verbosity levels are only guidelines to how a typical logger (including the default [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] console logger) logs build events.
trans-unit.target: Beskrivningar av hur nivåer är bara riktlinjer för hur en typisk transaktionsloggfiler (inklusive standard [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] konsolen transaktionsloggfiler) loggar skapa händelser.

trans-unit.source: Loggers are free to interpret verbosity levels in any way they want.
trans-unit.target: Loggar tangenttryckningar är gratis att tolka hur nivåer på något sätt som de vill.

trans-unit.source: Detailed verbosity, which displays errors, warnings, messages with <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.MessageImportance"></xref> values of <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.MessageImportance"></xref> or <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.MessageImportance"></xref>, all status events, and a build summary.
trans-unit.target: Mer detaljerad information, som visar fel, varningar, meddelanden med <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.MessageImportance"> </xref> värdena för <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.MessageImportance"> </xref> eller <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.MessageImportance"> </xref>, alla statushändelser och en build-sammanfattning.

trans-unit.source: Diagnostic verbosity, which displays all errors, warnings, messages, status events, and a build summary.
trans-unit.target: Diagnostisk information som visar alla fel, varningar, meddelanden, statushändelser och en build-sammanfattning.

trans-unit.source: Minimal verbosity, which displays errors, warnings, messages with <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.MessageImportance"></xref> values of <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.MessageImportance"></xref>, and a build summary.
trans-unit.target: Minimal information som visar fel, varningar, meddelanden med <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.MessageImportance"> </xref> värdena för <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.MessageImportance"> </xref>, och en build-sammanfattning.

trans-unit.source: Normal verbosity, which displays errors, warnings, messages with <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.MessageImportance"></xref> values of <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.MessageImportance"></xref>, some status events, and a build summary.
trans-unit.target: Normal information som visar fel, varningar, meddelanden med <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.MessageImportance"> </xref> värdena för <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Framework.MessageImportance"> </xref>, vissa statushändelser och en build-sammanfattning.

trans-unit.source: Quiet verbosity, which displays a build summary.
trans-unit.target: Tyst information som visar en sammanfattning av build.
